reviewText: Great storyline, great actors. I could identify with the characters and their individual story. Loved it.
I have watched Severed Ties twice and this is worth viewing.  It would be worth renting, but purchasing it, no.
A wonderful movie from the 90's.  I've always enjoyed this movie.  The Filmmaker was just recently interviewed at [...]Can't wait to see what they do next after a long break.
